	(text "Calcumaker 16 main — MCU (STM32U575ZGT6, LQFP-144). See DESIGN.md MCU + Pin Budget. Add: VDD/VDDA/VDDIO decoupling, LSE 32.768kHz + 2x load caps, NRST 100nF, BOOT0 10k pulldown, USB FS PA11/PA12 (ESD on PSU), SWD PA13/PA14 -> Tag-Connect, display bus (TM1640 2-wire: shared CLK + 3x DIN, 3V3 GPIO/bit-bang) -> Display-IF sheet (74HCT125 level shifter) + DISP_PWR_EN GPIO -> 5V boost EN, GPIO matrix -> Keypad sheet (one col -> EXTI wake)."
